properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island VA out 20 nm; Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 13 at 11:03AM EST until January 13 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to 1/2 NM or less.

* WHERE...Chesapeake Bay from Smith Point to Windmill Point VA
and Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island VA
out 20 nm.

* WHEN...Until 4 PM EST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
